 xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bhk1665702968969.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bhk1665702968969.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bhk1665702968969.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bhk1665702968969\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      upgrade locks\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Upgrade locking for existing tables to data pages, all pages, or row-level locking.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__topic_d60119e1_d60120e1_d60121e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60122e1_d60123e1_d60124e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= upgrade dpl</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">apl</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">locks</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__section_xct_mxw_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641754e69\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__ul_j52_nxw_jcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__li_d26693e1_d26694e1_d26695e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60128e1_d60129e1_d60130e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">dpl</code>—upgrade to data pages\n                  locking</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__li_d26696e1_d26697e1_d26698e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60131e1_d60132e1_d60133e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">apl</code>—upgrade to all pages\n                  locking</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__li_d26699e1_d26700e1_d26701e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60134e1_d60135e1_d60136e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">locks</code>—upgrade to row-level\n                  locking</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__section_e2y_nxw_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d641754e102\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60140e1_d60141e1_d60142e1\">When this options is enabled, the Create Table\n            facility creates SQL scripts to upgrade existing tables to the specified locking\n            level.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60143e1_d60144e1_d60145e1\">The Create Table facility modifies existing tables\n            rather than creating new tables, so you must stop and restart the Sybase SQL server\n            after running the SQL script in order for the server to recognize the change.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bhk1665702968969__p_d60146e1_d60147e1_d60148e1\">Use of the these option requires Sybase SQL Server\n            11.9.2 or higher.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bko1665702974302.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Upgrade to Row-Level, Data Pages, and All Pages Locking</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526055\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526055\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "upgrade locks Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 upgrade locks Upgrade locking for existing tables to data pages, all pages, or row-level locking. USYS$SYB_PARAMS = upgrade dpl | apl | locks Arguments dpl —upgrade to data pages locking apl —upgrade to all pages locking locks —upgrade to row-level locking Description When this options is enabled, the Create Table facility creates SQL scripts to upgrade existing tables to the specified locking level. The Create Table facility modifies existing tables rather than creating new tables, so you must stop and restart the Sybase SQL server after running the SQL script in order for the server to recognize the change. Use of the these option requires Sybase SQL Server 11.9.2 or higher. Related Links Upgrade to Row-Level, Data Pages, and All Pages Locking Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}